quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  20,112,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣe nínú àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, tí ó sì jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo, kí ó má ṣe páyà àbòsí tàbí ìrẹ́jẹ kan (láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu)."
  20,113,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe sọ (ìrántí) kalẹ̀ ní ohun kíké pẹ̀lú èdè Lárúbáwá. A sì ṣe àlàyé oníran-ànran ìlérí sínú rẹ̀ nítorí kí wọ́n lè ṣọ́ra (fún ìyà) tàbí nítorí kí ó lè jẹ́ ìrántí fún wọn."
  20,114,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu Ọba Òdodo ga jùlọ. Má ṣe kánjú pẹ̀lú al-Ƙur’ān ṣíwájú kí wọ́n tó parí ìmísí rẹ̀ fún ọ. Kí o sì sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, ṣàlékún ìmọ̀ fún mi.”"
  21,88,"A jẹ́pè rẹ̀. A sì gbà á là nínú ìbànújẹ́. Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń gba àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo là."
  21,89,"(Ẹ rántí Ànábì) Zakariyyā nígbà tí ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ pé: “Olúwa mi, má fi mí sílẹ̀ ní èmi nìkan (tí kò níí bímọ). Ìwọ sì lóore jùlọ nínú àwọn olùjogún.”1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah as-Sọffāt;  37:125.]
  21,90,"A jẹ́pè rẹ̀. A sì ta á lọ́rẹ ọmọ, (Ànábì) Yahyā. A sì ṣe àtúnṣe ìyàwó rẹ̀ fún un. Dájúdájú wọ́n ń yára gágá níbi àwọn iṣẹ́ rere. Wọ́n ń pè Wá pẹ̀lú ìrètí àti ìpáyà. Wọ́n sì jẹ́ olùtẹríba fún Wa."
  22,64,"TiRẹ̀ ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun mà ni Ọlọ́rọ̀, Ẹlẹ́yìn."
  22,65,"Ṣé o ò rí i pé dájúdájú Allāhu rọ ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ fún yín, àti ọkọ̀ ojú-omi tó ń rìn nínú agbami odò pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Rẹ̀, Ó ń mú sánmọ̀ dání tí kò fi jábọ́ àyàfi pẹ̀lú ìyọ̀ǹda Rẹ̀? Dájúdájú Allāhu mà ni Aláàánú, Oníkẹ̀ẹ́ fún àwọn ènìyàn."
  22,66,"Òun sì ni Ẹni tó ṣe yín ni alààyè, lẹ́yìn náà Ó ń sọ yín di òkú, lẹ́yìn náà Ó máa sọ yín di alààyè. Dájúdájú ènìyàn mà ni aláìmoore."
  23,40,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Láìpẹ́ ńṣe ni wọn yóò di alábàámọ̀.”"
  23,41,"Nítorí náà, ohùn igbe mú wọn ní ọ̀nà ẹ̀tọ́. A sì sọ wọ́n di pàǹtí. Nítorí náà, kí ìjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ wà fún ìjọ alábòsí."
  23,42,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tún mú àwọn ìran mìíràn wá lẹ́yìn wọn."
  24,22,"Kí àwọn tó ní ọlá àti ọrọ̀ púpọ̀ nínú yín má ṣe búra pé àwọn kò níí ṣe dáadáa sí àwọn ìbátan, àwọn mẹ̀kúnnù àti àwọn tó gbé ìlú wọn jù sílẹ̀ nítorí ẹ̀sìn Allāhu. Kí wọ́n ṣàforíjìn, kí wọ́n sì ṣàmójúkúrò. Ṣé ẹ kò fẹ́ kí Allāhu foríjìn yín ni? Allāhu sì ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  24,23,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ń parọ́ sìná mọ́ àwọn ọmọlúàbí lóbìnrin, àwọn tí sìná kò sí lórí ọkàn wọn, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo lóbìnrin, A ti ṣẹ́bilé wọn ní ayé àti ní ọ̀run. Ìyà ńlá sì wà fún wọn."
  24,24,"Ní ọjọ́ tí àwọn ahọ́n wọn, ọwọ́ wọn àti ẹsẹ̀ wọn yóò máa jẹ́rìí takò wọ́n nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́,"